module TopModule (
    input logic a,
    input logic b,
    input logic c,
    input logic d,
    output logic out
);

always @(*) begin
    out = (!c & !d & !a & !b) | 
          (!c & !d & !a & b) | 
          (!c & !d & a & !b) | 
          (!c & d & !a & !b) | 
          (!c & d & a & !b) | 
          (c & d & !a & b) | 
          (c & d & a & !b) | 
          (c & !d & !a & !b) | 
          (c & !d & !a & b);
end

endmodule
